<li id="cite_note-23"><b><a href="#cite_ref-23" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.snopes.com/politics/religion/fcc.asp" class="external text" title="http://www.snopes.com/politics/religion/fcc.asp" rel="nofollow">"Petition to Ban Religious Broadcasting"</a>. <i><a href="/wiki/Snopes" title="Snopes">Snopes</a></i><span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.snopes.com/politics/religion/fcc.asp" class="external free" title="http://www.snopes.com/politics/religion/fcc.asp" rel="nofollow">http://www.snopes.com/politics/religion/fcc.asp</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-12-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Petition+to+Ban+Religious+Broadcasting&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BSnopes%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.snopes.com%2Fpolitics%2Freligion%2Ffcc.asp&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Madalyn_Murray_O%27Hair"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
